Java Command Line Application for generating Yubikey-like OTP
===================================================

See COPYING for copyright information

Introduction
------------

This is a small command line application for generating Yubikey-like OTP on stdout


Building
--------

javac yubi_simulator.java

Background
----------

Find more about yubikeys at http://yubico.com

The idea of having the secret of an hardware OTP token on disk defeats the whole idea of it.
Nevertheless I found it useful to experiment with it and get more
insight on how it works.


